$ git branch -v
获得远程引用的完整列表
git ls-remote (remote)//origin
16ed15f3b69b30cb5eef76e8a212824ece8e41e1        HEAD
16ed15f3b69b30cb5eef76e8a212824ece8e41e1        refs/heads/master
